[[2019 Extra Life Donation Bundle]] is a [[Gem Store]] bundle, which was first released for the [[Extra Life]] [[Special event|special event]] in 2019.

== Acquisition ==
{{Sold by}}

== Contents ==
The contents are directly sent via an in-game mail titled "Delivery from: Black Lion Trading Company".
* {{contains|Mini Guardian Angel Aurene|chance=Guaranteed}}
* {{contains|Extra Life Karma Booster|chance=Guaranteed|qty=5}}
* {{contains|Temporary Selfless Potion|chance=Guaranteed|qty=5}}

== Notes ==
* Receiving the contents via an in-game mail grants the player the title {{flavor|The Extra Life}} in blue color.

